channel.title: Seeking past RuneScape caches
channel.description: Hello. I am currently looking for players who have quit RuneScape anytime from [b]April 9, 2008 to July 1, 2008[/b] and have not loaded the RuneScape login page since. Also if you had an old computer that you used during that time, and have never opened RuneScape since, you might have a rare RuneScape cache (#492~#499). You must have also been a member during that time, and logged into a member's world or it is incomplete. PLEASE post here if you do have a cache dating back to that time. It should be stored in your C:/ directory in a folder labeled ".jagex_cache_32". Thanks.
